Physics Informed Neural Network

Forward Problem
Solving the 1D Heat Equation

Possible File Structure:
pinn/
├── README.md
├── requirements.txt
├── src/
│   ├── model.py               # PINN class (nn.Module)
│   ├── physics.py             # PDE residual, BC/IC functions
│   ├── train.py               # training loop, Adam + L-BFGS
│   ├── sampling.py            # collocation point generation
│   └── utils.py               # device setup, seeding, plotting helpers
├── experiments/
│   ├── heat_1d.py             # one script per PDE/run
│   ├── oscillator.py
│   └── configs/               # YAML or dict configs per run
├── results/
│   ├── checkpoints/           # saved model weights (.pt files)
│   └── figures/               # generated plots
├── notebooks/
│   └── explore.ipynb          # sanity checks, quick viz
└── cpp/                       # later, for the C++ port
    └── ...